      <li><strong>Double-oven proactive hinge pair replacement.</strong> Lower fails first; we recommend both pairs past year 8 to save a callback.</li>
      <li><strong>Pro-tier vs mid-tier honest pricing.</strong> $600 to $900 pro-tier hinge replacement is real money, but on a $14,000+ unit with 18 to 25 year design life, it's the right call.</li>
      <li><strong>Built-in access labor quoted in writing.</strong> $200 to $400 uplift over free-standing range door work; no surprises after the cabinet opens.</li>
      <li><strong>Brand-specific gasket profiles.</strong> Miele continuous one-piece, Wolf multi-piece, mid-tier clip-in. We source the right gasket the first time.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS Licensed #A49573 and EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$89 residential diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/services/wall-oven-repair/not-heating/">not heating</a>, <a href="/services/wall-oven-repair/control-board-failure/">control board failure</a>, <a href="/services/wall-oven-repair/double-oven-issues/">double oven issues</a>. For free-standing range door diagnostic: <a href="/services/oven-repair/door-issues/">oven door issues</a>. Parent: <a href="/services/wall-oven-repair/">wall oven repair pillar</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

